          "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature in the area finishes an action</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The trap launches a targeted ad enticing viewers to spend credits on a product or service. All creatures within 30 feet who can see, hear, or sense the ad must attempt a @Check[will|dc:17] save. The trap rolls initiative.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> The target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TkIyaNPgTZFBCCuh]{Dazzled}.</p><p><strong>Failure</strong> The target is dazzled and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed 1}.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.AdPVz7rbaVSRxHFg]{Fascinated} for 1 round and can't take any actions except to access the nearest computer or comm unit and make purchases as directed by the ad.</p>",
